        <section>
            <title>Configuration</title>
            <para/>
            <section>
                <title>Building from Source</title>
                <para/>
                <example>
                    <title>extensions/local.build.properties</title>
                    <programlisting><![CDATA[#XSLT extension
include.feature.xslt = true
]]></programlisting>
                </example>
                <para>This extension compiles into <emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="italic"
                    >lib/extensions/exist-xslt.jar</emphasis></emphasis>.</para>
                
            </section>
            <section>
                <title>Enabling the Service</title>
                <para>This service is enabled by building the feature from source as described
                above and adding the following entry into webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml.</para>
                <example>
                    <title>webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml</title>
                    <programlisting format="linespecific">
                    <markup><![CDATA[    <servlet>
        <servlet-name>XSLTServlet</servlet-name>
        <servlet-class>org.exist.http.servlets.XSLTServlet</servlet-class>
    </servlet>]]></markup>
                </programlisting>
                </example>
                
            </section>
            <section>
                <title>Disabling the Service</title>
                <para>The only way to disable this service once it is enabled is to remove the
                    <emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="italic"
                        >lib/extensions/exist-xslt.jar</emphasis> and to remove the above entry from webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml</emphasis>
                    file.</para>
            </section>
        </section>
